title: Ep. - 238 - RORY FROM LOVE IS BLIND
description:
Abby Steffens reviews Busch Family Brewed on MTV, which features former owners of the Anheuser-Busch brewing company, Billy Sr. and Christi, alongside their seven children as they navigate their family legacy, relationship drama and new endeavors. 

 

Rory Newbrough from Love is Blind talks about his engagement, which was not featured on the show. He also explains how casting agents found the cast members, what happened inside the pods, and life after the show. 

 

 

Reality Life with Kate Casey
